f DJ=C2=A0D-Sol=E2=80=99s=C2=A0mixes and sent them to DJ critics, whose rea=
ctions ranged from positive:The [first] mix flows well with lots of energy =
and has a nice groove. Transitions and timings are pretty spot on so overal=
l strong mix for this type of genre. It=E2=80=99s just a bit too commercial=
