ild a set better and gain a deeper knowledge of dance music =E2=80=94 not j=
ust plump for obvious, commercial, accessible tracks. The person is obvious=
ly having fun, and I wouldn=E2=80=99t want to put anyone off. But without d=
emonstrating a knowledge of more quality and depth in their house music sel=
